content: {'id': '748768f9-9d84-363b-b8ad-f78dc1ce9697', 'contentType': 'STORY', 'title': "Max Healthcare, IndiGo parent to enter India's Nifty 50 index after rejig, NSE says", 'description': '', 'summary': "IndusInd Bank and Hero MotoCorp will be removed from the index as part of the NSE's semi-annual rebalancing, the exchange said.
